control + D = multiple selection of same words.
control + V = duplication of same line in which the cursor is present.
shift + alt + arrow key = duplication of same line in which the cursor is present.
control + X = to cut the same line.
shift + alt + mouse selection
alt + click (mouse click)
control + F = to check the number of occurence of words.
(control + shift + L) OR (control + f2) = at a time selection of the same word.